Class StevensonReading

    WeatherReading

    public final class StevensonReading
extends java.lang.Object
implements WeatherReading
    StevensonReading represented as temperature, dew point, wind speed and total rain. StevensonReading calculated to get relative humidity, heat index and wind chill.
